QuestionDef.QText: Is application face page dated and signed?
Does IRB approval date precede institutional official's signature date?
Exemption number OR IRB approval date given?
Is IRB approval date within 12 months prior to start date?
FWA/MPA number same as number on file with OHRP?
Does IACUC approval date precede institutional official's signature date?
Is IACUC approval date within 36 months prior to start date?
Is Animal Welfare Assurance number given?
Is Face Page signed and dated by required officials?
